title: El nuevo trailer de Capitana Marvel, rompe Internet| #Cine
body:
El nuevo trailer de Capitana Marvel, rompe Internet| #Cine

Que tal a toda la banda de MultiAnime!

Hace unas horas se liberó el tercer trailer de Captain Marvel, mostrando nuevas escenas de la película, dando más información acerca de la historia, así como la relación que tendrá con Nick Fury, además de que vemos más líneas del Agente Coulson, haciendo referencia a Avengers.

Es un excelente material promocional para calmar las ansias, ya que todavía falta…

body:
Samuel L. Jackson Reveals Captain Marvel Can Time Travel

Samuel L. Jackson, who plays Nick Fury in the Marvel Cinematic Universe, just revealed that Captain Marvel has the ability to time travel.

In an interview with E! Online, Jackson boasted about Captain Marvel’s intense powers.

“She’s pretty much the strongest character in terms of someone with powers that are able to do things in the Marvel Universe, so for Carol Danvers to be that person—and for…

summary: I’m Talos. I’m the battle commander of the Skrulls. I take it most of you know who Skrulls are? We kind of rule the shit. Most...
text: I’m Talos. I’m the battle commander of the Skrulls. I take it most of you know who Skrulls are? We kind of rule the shit. Most of the rest of the Marvel comic universe are punks basically. And I guess to quote Snoop Dogg, we are the shiznit. We stand above. I mean, look, we can be anyone, and we’re stronger than the rest of them. Basically that’s it. Yeah, we’re maligned, we’re misunderstood. But, you know, we’re Skrulls. We’re Skrullin. Any other questions?
